I missed one of my connecting flights,

00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:09.200
I had to get off the airplane and&nbsp;
recheck my bag because apparently&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:01:09.200 --> 00:01:12.560
if you're in another country for over 2&nbsp;
hours, then you have to recheck your bag–

