For context, a business class flight from LA&nbsp;
to Switzerland non-stop costs $7,000 one way

00:01:34.560 --> 00:01:37.840
But with the bid upgrade, how it works is you bid&nbsp;
how much you'd be willing to pay for an upgrade

00:01:37.840 --> 00:01:41.120
